---
import BaseLayout from "../../layout/BaseLayout.astro";

const mailto = "mailto:hey@thefocus.ai?subject=Monthly%20Close%20-%20Build%20%26%20Ship";
---

<BaseLayout
  pageTitle="AI-Powered Monthly Close | TheFocus.AI"
  description="Your monthly close shouldn't take 10 days. We formalize the tribal knowledge in your close process and build AI systems that reconcile, flag anomalies, and route approvals automatically."
  category="capabilities"
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="py-8 md:py-16">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
        <span class="text-xs font-mono text-graphite border border-ink/15 px-2 py-1 rounded">L1 &rarr; L2</span>
        <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-petrol font-medium">Process Audit + Knowledge Layer</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 text-ink leading-tight">
        Your Monthly Close Shouldn't Take 10 Days
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-graphite leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-3xl">
        Every finance team knows the drill: reconcile across disconnected systems, chase down approvals, manually check entries, and hope nothing slips through. One person's absence breaks the whole timeline. It doesn't have to work this way.
      </p>
      <a
        href={mailto}
        class="inline-block px-8 py-4 bg-petrol text-paper font-medium uppercase text-sm tracking-wider rounded-full hover:bg-petrol/90 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-200"
      >
        Discuss Your Close Process &rarr;
      </a>
    </section>

    <!-- Video -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <div class="relative aspect-video rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
        <video
          autoplay
          muted
          playsinline
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          poster="/videos/offerings/monthly-close.mp4#t=0.1"
        >
          <source src="/videos/offerings/monthly-close.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
        </video>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- The Pain -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-petrol mb-6 font-medium">The Problem</h2>
      <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-ink mb-8">Sound familiar?</h3>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start p-4 rounded-xl bg-tint-warm/30">
          <span class="text-vermilion font-bold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">&times;</span>
          <p class="text-graphite">Reconciliation across GL, sub-ledgers, and bank statements is manual — and it takes the first 3-4 days of every close.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start p-4 rounded-xl bg-tint-warm/30">
          <span class="text-vermilion font-bold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">&times;</span>
          <p class="text-graphite">Journal entries require hand-checking because the rules live in one person's head — the person who's been doing it for 8 years.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start p-4 rounded-xl bg-tint-warm/30">
          <span class="text-vermilion font-bold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">&times;</span>
          <p class="text-graphite">Approval routing is a chain of emails and Slack messages. When someone's on vacation, the whole process stalls.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start p-4 rounded-xl bg-tint-warm/30">
          <span class="text-vermilion font-bold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">&times;</span>
          <p class="text-graphite">Audit prep is a quarterly fire drill — you're rebuilding the paper trail from scratch every time because it wasn't captured as you went.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- The Approach -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <div class="border-l-4 border-petrol bg-paper rounded-r-2xl p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm">
        <h2 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-petrol mb-4 font-medium">Our Approach</h2>
        <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-ink mb-4">How we fix this</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-petrol/80 mb-4">A Habitat is a production AI system that carries your team's rules, learns from decisions, and runs autonomously.</p>
        <p class="text-graphite leading-relaxed mb-6">
          We build an agent habitat — a system that carries the state of your close process, accumulates institutional memory, and matures from guided workflow to automated execution. The close checklist, exception rules, and approval logic that currently live in people's heads get formalized into a system that runs reliably every month.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-petrol/10 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-sm font-mono font-bold text-petrol">1</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-ink mb-1">Discover</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-graphite">We audit your actual close process — not the documented version, the real one. Every workaround, exception, and judgment call gets mapped.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-petrol/10 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-sm font-mono font-bold text-petrol">2</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-ink mb-1">Structure</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-graphite">Reconciliation rules, cost code mappings, and approval thresholds get formalized into schemas and validation rules that machines can follow.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-petrol/10 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-sm font-mono font-bold text-petrol">3</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-ink mb-1">Build</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-graphite">An AI system that reconciles across your GL and sub-ledgers, flags anomalies with explanations, routes approvals automatically, and builds the audit trail as it goes.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Proof Points -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-petrol mb-6 font-medium">Proof</h2>
      <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-ink mb-8">We've done this before</h3>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <a href="/case-study/qbsync" class="group block border border-ink/10 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:border-petrol/30 transition-all">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-petrol mb-2">57,000</p>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-ink mb-2">transactions synced automatically</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-graphite mb-3">QB Sync — automated construction project accounting from QuickBooks to Google Sheets. Tribal cost codes discovered and formalized into machine-readable rules.</p>
          <span class="text-petrol text-sm font-medium group-hover:underline">Read case study &rarr;</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/case-study/fountain-creek" class="group block border border-ink/10 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:border-petrol/30 transition-all">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-petrol mb-2">94.5%</p>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-ink mb-2">validated accuracy on invoice parsing</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-graphite mb-3">Fountain Creek — AI-powered accounts payable for multi-location food service. Varied supplier invoices parsed and structured automatically.</p>
          <span class="text-petrol text-sm font-medium group-hover:underline">Read case study &rarr;</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Related Offerings -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-graphite/60 mb-4 font-medium">Related Offerings</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
        <a href="/offerings/invoice-processing" class="group flex items-center gap-3 p-4 rounded-xl border border-ink/8 hover:border-petrol/30 hover:bg-tint-cool/20 transition-all">
          <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-ink group-hover:text-petrol transition-colors">Invoice / AP Processing</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-graphite">Handle any vendor format automatically</p>
          </div>
          <span class="text-petrol/40 group-hover:text-petrol transition-colors flex-shrink-0">&rarr;</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/offerings/executive-reporting" class="group flex items-center gap-3 p-4 rounded-xl border border-ink/8 hover:border-petrol/30 hover:bg-tint-cool/20 transition-all">
          <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-ink group-hover:text-petrol transition-colors">Executive Reporting</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-graphite">Real-time answers, not reformatted dashboards</p>
          </div>
          <span class="text-petrol/40 group-hover:text-petrol transition-colors flex-shrink-0">&rarr;</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="border-t border-ink/10 pt-16 pb-8">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <span class="text-xs font-mono text-graphite border border-ink/15 px-2 py-1 rounded">Build & Ship</span>
        <span class="text-xs font-medium text-graphite">2-6 weeks</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-ink">Ready to close the books faster?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-graphite mb-8 max-w-2xl">
        The conversation starts with understanding your current close process — the real version, not the documented one.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
        <a
          href={mailto}
          class="inline-block px-8 py-4 bg-petrol text-paper font-medium uppercase text-sm tracking-wider rounded-full hover:bg-petrol/90 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-200 text-center"
        >
          Start a Conversation
        </a>
        <a
          href="/capabilities"
          class="inline-block px-8 py-4 border-2 border-ink/20 text-ink font-medium uppercase text-sm tracking-wider rounded-full hover:border-petrol hover:text-petrol hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-200 text-center"
        >
          See the Full Framework
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>
